<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Storyboard 2 — Robert</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; background-color: #f5f0e8; color: #1a1a1a; }
    .top-nav { background-color: #fff; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px 0; font-size: 0.8rem; }
    .top-nav a { color: #1a6b3a; text-decoration: none; }
    .top-nav a:hover { color: #1a1a1a; }
    h1 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; }
    .persona-card { background-color: #fff; border-left: 3px solid #1a6b3a; padding: 22px 24px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .persona-card h5 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; color: #1a6b3a; }
    .persona-card p, .persona-card li { font-size: 0.88rem; color: #555; }
    .step-num { font-size: 0.72rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: #1a6b3a; font-weight: 600; }
    .step-card { background-color: #fff; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 0; }
    .step-card .mockup { background-color: #f0ebe0; padding: 20px; min-height: 220px; }
    .step-card .caption { padding: 16px 18px; }
    .step-card .caption h6 { font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .step-card .caption p { font-size: 0.84rem; color: #666; margin: 0; }
    .mock-nav { background: #fff; height: 32px; border-radius: 2px; margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 0 10px; gap: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; }
    .mock-nav .logo { font-size: 0.7rem; color: #1a1a1a; font-weight: 600; }
    .mock-nav span { font-size: 0.62rem; color: #999; }
    .mock-hero { background: #1a1a1a; border-radius: 2px; padding: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .mock-hero .h { height: 8px; background: #f5f0e8; border-radius: 1px; width: 55%; margin-bottom: 5px; }
    .mock-hero .sub { height: 5px; background: #555; border-radius: 1px; width: 75%; }
    .mock-service-row { display: flex; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .mock-service-item { flex: 1; height: 50px; background: #fff; border-radius: 2px; border-left: 2px solid #1a6b3a; padding: 6px; }
    .mock-service-item .price { height: 8px; background: #1a6b3a; border-radius: 1px; width: 40%; }
    .mock-service-item .label { height: 5px; background: #ccc; border-radius: 1px; width: 70%; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .mock-contact { background: #fff; border-radius: 2px; padding: 12px; }
    .mock-contact-row { display: flex; gap: 8px; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .mock-contact-row .dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; background: #1a6b3a; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .mock-contact-row .line { height: 6px; background: #ddd; border-radius: 1px; flex: 1; }
    .mock-hours { background: #f5f0e8; padding: 8px; border-radius: 2px; }
    .mock-hours-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 5px; }
    .mock-hours-row .day { height: 5px; background: #999; border-radius: 1px; width: 35%; }
    .mock-hours-row .time { height: 5px; background: #bbb; border-radius: 1px; width: 45%; }
    .arrow { color: #1a6b3a; font-size: 1.5rem; text-align: center; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="top-nav">
  <div class="container d-flex justify-content-between">
    <a href="../index.html">← Back to Portfolio</a>
    <span style="color:#aaa;">Storyboard 2 of 2</span>
    <a href="storyboard1.html">← Storyboard 1</a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container py-5">
  <p style="font-size:0.75rem; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.15em; color:#1a6b3a; font-weight:600;">Assignment 2 — SEG3125</p>
  <h1 style="font-size:2.2rem; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Storyboard 2 — Persona: Robert</h1>
  <p style="color:#888; font-size:0.92rem; margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Light theme · Desktop · Goal: Find address, hours, and pricing</p>

  <div class="persona-card">
    <h5>Robert, 54 — Accountant</h5>
    <ul>
      <li>Not very tech-savvy, prefers simple pages with clear information</li>
      <li>Patient but gets confused by cluttered or busy layouts</li>
      <li>Long-time barbershop customer — goes every two to three weeks</li>
    </ul>
    <p style="margin:0;"><strong>Goal:</strong> Check the prices, find the address, and see what hours the shop is open.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="row align-items-center g-4">
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <p class="step-num">Step 01</p>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="mockup">
          <div class="mock-nav"><span class="logo">PrestigeCuts</span><span>Services</span><span>Book</span><span>Contact</span></div>
          <div class="mock-hero">
            <div class="h"></div>
            <div class="sub"></div>
          </div>
          <div style="height:8px; background:#ddd; border-radius:1px; width:90%; margin-bottom:8px;"></div>
          <div style="height:8px; background:#ddd; border-radius:1px; width:70%;"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="caption">
          <h6>Lands on homepage</h6>
          <p>Robert opens the site from a coworker's recommendation. Reads the hero text, starts scrolling.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-1 d-none d-md-block arrow">→</div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <p class="step-num">Step 02</p>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="mockup">
          <div class="mock-nav"><span class="logo">PrestigeCuts</span></div>
          <div style="height:6px; background:#1a6b3a; border-radius:1px; width:30%; margin-bottom:8px; opacity:0.6;"></div>
          <div style="height:9px; background:#333; border-radius:1px; width:50%; margin-bottom:12px;"></div>
          <div class="mock-service-row">
            <div class="mock-service-item"><div class="label"></div><div class="price"></div></div>
            <div class="mock-service-item"><div class="label"></div><div class="price"></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="mock-service-row">
            <div class="mock-service-item"><div class="label"></div><div class="price"></div></div>
            <div class="mock-service-item"><div class="label"></div><div class="price"></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="caption">
          <h6>Checks services and pricing</h6>
          <p>Scrolls to the services section. Sees Classic Haircut for $35 and the Combo for $55. Decides the combo is worth it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-1 d-none d-md-block arrow">→</div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <p class="step-num">Step 03</p>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="mockup">
          <div class="mock-nav"><span class="logo">PrestigeCuts</span></div>
          <div style="display:flex; gap:12px; margin-top:6px;">
            <div style="flex:1;">
              <div class="mock-contact">
                <div class="mock-contact-row"><div class="dot"></div><div class="line"></div></div>
                <div class="mock-contact-row"><div class="dot"></div><div class="line" style="width:60%;"></div></div>
                <div class="mock-contact-row"><div class="dot"></div><div class="line" style="width:75%;"></div></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div style="flex:1;">
              <div class="mock-hours">
                <div class="mock-hours-row"><div class="day"></div><div class="time"></div></div>
                <div class="mock-hours-row"><div class="day"></div><div class="time"></div></div>
                <div class="mock-hours-row"><div class="day"></div><div class="time"></div></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="caption">
          <h6>Finds address and hours</h6>
          <p>Scrolls to the Contact section. Gets the address and confirms they're open on Saturdays. Plans to walk in.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-5 pt-3 border-top d-flex gap-4" style="font-size:0.82rem;">
    <a href="../service-site.html" style="color:#1a6b3a; text-decoration:none;">View Live Site →</a>
    <a href="storyboard1.html" style="color:#888; text-decoration:none;">← Storyboard 1</a>
    <a href="../index.html" style="color:#888; text-decoration:none;">Portfolio →</a>
  </div>
</div>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
